  construction induces a functor `‚à´(G ‚ãô F) ‚•§ ‚à´(F)`. -/
def pre : ‚à´(G ‚ãô F) ‚•§ ‚à´(F) :=
  Grothendieck.pre (F ‚ãô Grpd.forgetToCat) G

@[simp]
